{
  "id": "69feb0d6494124d563efa6d1",
  "title": "簡単な卵料理",
  "created": 1778299109,
  "updated": 1778300102,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69feb0d6494124d563efa6d1",
      "text": "簡単な卵料理",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299109,
      "updated": 1778299109
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb0d60000000000ad74e4",
      "text": "from [2026/05/09]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299109,
      "updated": 1778299109
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb0d60000000000ad74e5",
      "text": "簡単な[卵料理]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299109,
      "updated": 1778299149
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb0d60000000000ad74e6",
      "text": "あるのか？[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299109,
      "updated": 1778299136
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb0d60000000000ad74e7",
      "text": " 卵料理だいたいむずい、ポーチドエッグとか最高にむずい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299109,
      "updated": 1778299167
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb12000000000005f2ce3",
      "text": "  ゆでたまごはゆでたまご蒸し器があるので作れる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299168,
      "updated": 1778299185
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb30300000000005f2ce5",
      "text": "  考えてみたけど、卵の黄身を半熟にしたまま白身に火を通そうとする試みが卵料理の難しさを上げている",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299651,
      "updated": 1778299702
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb0d60000000000ad74e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299109,
      "updated": 1778299109
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb1240000000000eae482",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299172,
      "updated": 1778299172
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb11a0000000000eae480",
      "text": "レンチンでジェネリック[卵サンド][terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299163,
      "updated": 1778299363
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb12a0000000000eae483",
      "text": "\tここ数ヶ月くらいマイブームのやつ",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299178,
      "updated": 1778299190
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb1380000000000eae484",
      "text": "\t1. 卵3つ割りほぐして、卵の殻半分ぶんくらいの水をいれて混ぜて、レンチン500W 1分40秒。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299193,
      "updated": 1778299343
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb1400000000000eae485",
      "text": "\t\t[脱線.icon]昔、レシピ本かなんかで初めて[割りほぐす]って見て、なんやそれ知らん単語使うな！ってつっこんだ思い出。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299201,
      "updated": 1778299426
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb1790000000000eae486",
      "text": "\t2. 箸で混ぜて、再度40秒レンチン",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299258,
      "updated": 1778299285
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb1950000000000eae487",
      "text": "\t3. 塩をひとつまみ、マヨネーズを大さじ2くらい入れて混ぜる",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299286,
      "updated": 1778299305
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb1a90000000000eae488",
      "text": "\t4. スプーンで食パンに載せて食う（面倒になって卵サンドにはしなくなった）。ウマー",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299306,
      "updated": 1778299389
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb1eb00000000005f2ce4",
      "text": "\tおいしそう[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778299371,
      "updated": 1778299383
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb11e0000000000eae481",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778299170,
      "updated": 1778299170
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb4b3000000000073a846",
      "text": "[卵料理の難しさ、卵を割る段階から始まっていた]（2026/05/09）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778300084,
      "updated": 1778300102
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb3c0000000000073a840",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778299841,
      "updated": 1778299841
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb3c1000000000073a841",
      "text": "卵焼き意外と難しい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778299842,
      "updated": 1778299861
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb3c8000000000073a842",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778299849,
      "updated": 1778299849
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb3f0000000000073a843",
      "text": "卵かけご飯をファイナルアンサーにしよう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778299889,
      "updated": 1778299912
    },
    {
      "id": "69feb3f1000000000073a844",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778299890,
      "updated": 1778299890
    }
  ]
}